title: ALPHA MALES #5 BRUTAL CLUBHOUSE LOVE!: A sissy's rough journey to submission
description: Tyler's in a hard place.  Dressed in women's underwear, trapped in a motorcycle gang clubhouse, he's surrounded by mean biker's who learned about guy on guy love in prison. Bottoms are all bottom, tops are all top. He's going to have to make it with another sissy, take the mutant-sized meat pole of a gang enforcer, and then submit to every club member, one after the other, or two and three at a time.  If he doesn't do a good job he might not make it out alive.  This is what it's like to be a power bottom in BRUTAL CLUBHOUSE LOVE!
author: Vixen Wade
